        "content": "## Description:\nThis workflow gets the latest workflow version and compares it to version on Github. Based on version & if file exists different outcomes apply",
        "height": 112,
        "width": 400,
        "color": 5
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [-528, -352],
